Definition: a Gestalt principle of organization holding that aspects of perceptual field that move or function in a similar manner will be perceived as a unit
Synonyms: law_of_common_fate, Gestalt_law_of_organization, a, Gestalt, principle, of, organization, holding, that, aspects, perceptual, field, move, or, function, in, similar, manner, will, be, perceived, as, unit
Category: noun.cognition
